{"tid":1767632,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"KKday 海洋公園買一送一苦主圍爐區","createTime":"2019-12-03T12:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T15:52:28.000Z","uid":123922,"like":266,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"b3cb9e84c5146d84a0bc1406f66a7ee55bdfa25e","tid":1767632,"uid":123922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:33:59.000Z","msg":"首先一早同咗大家講kkday哩間奶共閪野要罷買（詳情可以起底睇我之前既post)<br />\n點知見到佢推啲優惠 一大堆人衝去搶<br />\n好啦 宜家kkday柒咗啦 見到大量苦主俾人呃<br />\n所以係到俾各苦主一個方法啦<br />\n<br />\n消委會投訴<br />\n消委會幫到你~ 不過留意番, KKDAY冇旅遊牌架!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.consumer.org.hk/ws_chi/cc-complaint/index.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.consumer.org.hk%2Fws_chi%2Fcc-complaint%2Findex.php&d=QAb612WS2prazXX2mE0Ksad04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=f3988fe7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.consumer.org.hk/ws_chi/cc-complaint/index.php</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HfVxgEP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHfVxgEP.jpg&h=ecf7be41&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7gro7Mu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7gro7Mu.jpg&h=a23a19da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V6ak9ZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV6ak9ZQ.jpg&h=07ffa658&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g8AJojQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg8AJojQ.jpg&h=0ed8b218&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AidOzry.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAidOzry.png&h=9f36b410&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oVdSgET.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoVdSgET.jpg&h=9ac22f84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，李靜茵你條仆街冚家剷，秋後算賬班黃絲手足你就叻，搞小小優惠都搞到成pat屎咁，唔駛問聽日你又屌鳩班下屬係垃圾啦，負責哩壇野既員工等俾人屌到喊啦"},{"pid":"4d7ee6079ec4bc0116691a639a913cb2910519de","tid":1767632,"uid":140953,"like":231,"dislike":3,"score":228,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:38:57.000Z","msg":"睇完都唔知發生咩事"},{"pid":"22e3d1b507cc5fed8382e49b3faa87cacfbb3b13","tid":1767632,"uid":123922,"like":70,"dislike":5,"score":65,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:39:27.000Z","msg":"推啦 大家肯罷買kkday未<br />\n搵人新增去罷買list please <br />\n香港人場運動未完架<br />\n要堅持"},{"pid":"507460c23273cd82ad9926492decd5b37dfeb44c","tid":1767632,"uid":103936,"like":226,"dislike":8,"score":218,"quote":{"pid":"4d7ee6079ec4bc0116691a639a913cb2910519de","tid":1767632,"uid":140953,"like":231,"dislike":3,"score":228,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:38:57.000Z","msg":"睇完都唔知發生咩事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:43:17.000Z","msg":"1 藍底平台搞OP買一送一<br />\n2 貪心小狗 狗衝buy one 期望get one free<br />\n3 搞手話其實要買二 再whatsapp定乜柒抽獎 中獎先get one free<br />\n4 貪字得個貧嘅苦主叫春<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774d593abc83a79b06e030a1413a3ccf0be6398e","tid":1767632,"uid":33359,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:43:24.000Z","msg":"苦主師將會全面進場"},{"pid":"b1bc2973bdf80c5b65fff4515ca65b7314ea3877","tid":1767632,"uid":235801,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"22e3d1b507cc5fed8382e49b3faa87cacfbb3b13","tid":1767632,"uid":123922,"like":70,"dislike":5,"score":65,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:39:27.000Z","msg":"推啦 大家肯罷買kkday未<br />\n搵人新增去罷買list please <br />\n香港人場運動未完架<br />\n要堅持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:43:38.000Z","msg":"啫個意思係，依家係俾錢買個優惠而唔係買緊張飛？"},{"pid":"51d2f350c703d3f18c4eae1c8c380b97dfbf0b4b","tid":1767632,"uid":219564,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:44:31.000Z","msg":"屌你老母呢間野奶共㗎"},{"pid":"b262027a621dbaa52c4b28732edc15c00306c34f","tid":1767632,"uid":123922,"like":88,"dislike":2,"score":86,"quote":{"pid":"4d7ee6079ec4bc0116691a639a913cb2910519de","tid":1767632,"uid":140953,"like":231,"dislike":3,"score":228,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:38:57.000Z","msg":"睇完都唔知發生咩事"},"citedBy":2,"re